* SURBEY
1. 현재 귀하는 어느 분야에 종사하고 계십니까? - 일 경험 없음
2. 현재 귀하는 학생이십니까? - 아니오
3. 현재 귀하는 어디에 살고 계십니까? - 개인주택이나 아파트에 홀로 거주
4. 귀하는 여가 활동으로 주로 무엇을 하십니까? - 영화보기, 콘서트보기, 공연보기, 캠핑하기, 공원가기, 해변가기 (6)
5. 귀하의 취미나 관심사는 무엇입니까? - 음악 감상하기 (1)
6. 귀하는 주로 어떤 운동을 즐기십니까? - 조깅, 걷기, 운동을 전혀 하지 않음 (3)
7. 귀하는 어떤 휴가나 출장을 다녀온 경험이 있습니까? - 국내 여행, 해외 여행 (4)


* 자기소개

* 날씨
Description) What is the weather like in your country?  Are there distinct changes in the seasons?  
             Describe what the weather is like in the summer.  What is the weather like in the winter?  
             Provide a detailed description of each of the four seasons.

Description) Identify your favorite season and describe some of the activities that you do during this time of year.


Description) Discuss a memorable event in your life that you either heard about or experienced firsthand that was associated with weather in some way.  
             For instance, it may have been a drought that affected the people in your town or a flood that you read about that caused many to lose their homes. 
             Describe the event, when it occurred and all of the details that you remembered about it.



